# Gauge.SU2

SU(2) gauge algebra.

The SU(2) gauge algebra is su(2) ≅ A₁ (rank-1 simple Lie algebra), spanned by
generators T₁, T₂, T₃ with:
  [T₁, T₂] = i T₃,  [T₂, T₃] = i T₁,  [T₃, T₁] = i T₂

In the Standard Model, SU(2)_L is the weak isospin gauge factor acting on
left-handed fermion doublets.

Status: stub.
